KPC <%= @trip.number %> - One Month Out!

Hey <%= @golfer.nickname %>,

We're one month out from KPC <%= @trip.number %> in <%= @trip.location %>! You're all paid up. Thanks for getting your money in on time! Here's a reminder of what you signed up for:

YOUR ITINERARY
<% if @nights.any? %>
Nights:
<% @nights.each do |night| %>
  <%= night.date.strftime("%A, %B %-d") %> — $<%= number_with_delimiter(night.cost) %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @rounds.any? %>
Rounds:
<% @rounds.each do |round| %>
  <%= round.date.strftime("%A, %B %-d") %> — <%= round.cost == 0 ? "à la carte" : "$#{number_with_delimiter(round.cost)}" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

See you in <%= @trip.location %>!
